                            <comment id="14602170" author="x1" created="Fri, 26 Jun 2015 00:18:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think &lt;tt&gt;sorter.cleanupAfterError()&lt;/tt&gt; throw &lt;tt&gt;SparkException&lt;/tt&gt;, - not &lt;tt&gt;IOException&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
But method &lt;tt&gt;write&lt;/tt&gt; declare throw &lt;tt&gt;IOException&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; void write(scala.collection.Iterator&amp;lt;Product2&amp;lt;K, V&amp;gt;&amp;gt; records) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;throws&lt;/span&gt; IOException
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So, maybe we cannot compile &lt;tt&gt;UnsafeShuffleWriter&lt;/tt&gt; class.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
